# Confidence Book v2.0 - Environment Variables

# ========== DATABASE (Turso) ==========
# Create free account: https://turso.tech
# Commands:
#   turso db create confidence-book
#   turso db show confidence-book
DATABASE_URL=libsql://your-database.turso.io
DATABASE_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token_here

# ========== AI MODERATION (Groq - Free) ==========
# Create free account: https://console.groq.com
# Get API Key (free with LLaMA models)
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_api_key_here

# ========== NOTES ==========
# - NEVER commit .env file (already in .gitignore)
# - On Render/Railway, add these in Environment Variables settings
# - PORT is automatically provided by hosting platform
# - In development without API keys, moderation will be skipped